QuestData.Title: The Coast Isn't Clear
QuestData.Description: You probably noticed all of the shipwrecks along the coast. The Great Sea is treacherous indeed. The coast of Westfall needs to be kept clear, so that if sailors find their way to our beaches, they are safe. The Murlocs are trouble though.$b$bKill murloc tidehunters and oracles and I will see to it that you are rewarded.
QuestData.LogDescription: Kill 7 Murloc Tidehunters and 7 Murloc Oracles.
QuestData.RewardText: Well done, $n. You have quite a knack for combat. Thanks to you the Coast of Westfall is a safer place.
